              <div class="answer"><p>If CRA reviews or audits a return Yarova prepared, we respond on your behalf &mdash; letters, document submissions, follow-up calls, the full back-and-forth &mdash; at no additional charge. Most accounting firms bill $150&ndash;$400/hour for representation. We include it because it&rsquo;s the only honest interpretation of &ldquo;flat fee.&rdquo;</p></div>
